This sample code is built to generate a range of sine tone, from 10Hz to 44kHz.

The first draft of code stimulated from the post at
http://marblemice.blogspot.com/2010/04/generate-and-play-tone-in-android.html
and 
http://audioprograming.wordpress.com/2012/10/18/a-simple-synth-in-android-step-by-step-guide-using-the-java-sdk/

Also refered to another blog
http://webtutsdepot.com/2011/12/03/android-sdk-tutorial-seekbar-example/
to create the slider bar.
